ill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3945f34a24c766abe198231409bbd68d183fe4f0","tid":1455463,"uid":266683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:04:22.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撚完狗，呢度走</span></span><br />\n機場T1 抵港大堂疏散路線<br />\n-<br />\n藍線為大路，有機會被警察部防封鎖。<br />\n紅線為緊急逃生路線，已查証可繼續通行。<br />\n切記不要進入禁區，如需要出示passport及boarding pass的地方，因機場特警係可以合理執法。<br />\n<br />\n#現場情況<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXfw0j1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXfw0j1.jpg&h=6d1629d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ea3828b95145dd4956e75a059e2846b6ffe5f3c","tid":1455463,"uid":288924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d218b6df01f04864f24d1740f9d3908891ca3c","tid":1455463,"uid":288924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da5c536e56fd87d4e8fbad4e97b2f81ac86ead9","tid":1455463,"uid":113784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:04:47.000Z","msg":"1. 我哋目的係向外宣傳，冇機冇旅客，等於冇宣傳<br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋目的可能係癱瘓機場，依家所有班機都取消，已經癱瘓咗機場<br />\n<br />\n留低有咩做？？自己問下自己。<br />\n<br />\n到時機場回復運作咪再入過囉，更加唔好講夜晚收工接力的手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84f